[
  {
    "startTime": 0.1,
    "endTime": 5.31,
    "text": "Please try to understand. I've never done a thing on my own."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.31,
    "endTime": 8.7,
    "text": "I've never had any real friends."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.7,
    "endTime": 11.399999999999999,
    "text": "Except you, Raja."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.4,
    "endTime": 14.46,
    "text": "I've never even been outside the palace walls."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.46,
    "endTime": 17.0,
    "text": "But Jasmine, you're a princess."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.0,
    "endTime": 23.3,
    "text": "Then maybe I don't wanna be a princess anymore."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.3,
    "endTime": 26.8,
    "text": "Oh, you must be hungry, here you go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.8,
    "endTime": 30.310000000000002,
    "text": "You'd better be able to pay for that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.31,
    "endTime": 31.0,
    "text": "Pay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.0,
    "endTime": 34.0,
    "text": "No one steals from my cart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.7,
    "endTime": 36.434000000000005,
    "text": "I'm sorry, sir, I don't have any money."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.434,
    "endTime": 36.9,
    "text": "Thief."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.0,
    "endTime": 41.0,
    "text": "Please, if you let me go to the palace I can get some from the Sultan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.0,
    "endTime": 44.26,
    "text": "Do you know what the penalty is for stealing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.26,
    "endTime": 46.21,
    "text": "No, no, please."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.21,
    "endTime": 50.05,
    "text": "Thank you, kind sir, I'm so glad you found her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.05,
    "endTime": 51.3,
    "text": "I've been looking all over for you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.3,
    "endTime": 52.352,
    "text": "What are you doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.0,
    "endTime": 53.0,
    "text": "Just play along."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.0,
    "endTime": 55.5,
    "text": "You know this girl?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.5,
    "endTime": 58.5,
    "text": "Sadly yes, she is my sister."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.5,
    "endTime": 60.23,
    "text": "She's a little crazy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.23,
    "endTime": 63.099999999999994,
    "text": "She said she knew the Sultan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.1,
    "endTime": 68.0,
    "text": "She thinks the monkey is the Sultan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.0,
    "endTime": 72.812,
    "text": "Oh wise Sultan, how may I serve you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.01,
    "endTime": 77.10000000000001,
    "text": "Tragic, isn't it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.1,
    "endTime": 82.1,
    "text": "But no harm done. Now come along sis, time to go see the doctor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.1,
    "endTime": 84.47999999999999,
    "text": "Oh hello doctor, how are you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.48,
    "endTime": 86.7,
    "text": "No no no, not that one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.7,
    "endTime": 91.8,
    "text": "Come on Sultan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.0,
    "endTime": 93.3,
    "text": "What..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.3,
    "endTime": 97.371,
    "text": "Come back here, you little thieves."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.24,
    "endTime": 107.07,
    "text": "I want to thank you for stopping that man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.07,
    "endTime": 110.0,
    "text": "Forget it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.0,
    "endTime": 113.266,
    "text": "So this is your first time in the marketplace, huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.37,
    "endTime": 117.4,
    "text": "Is it that obvious?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.4,
    "endTime": 121.30000000000001,
    "text": "Welll, you do kind of stand out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.5,
    "endTime": 127.5,
    "text": "I mean, you don't seem to know how dangerous Agrabah can be."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.5,
    "endTime": 131.09,
    "text": "I'm a fast learner."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.09,
    "endTime": 133.45000000000002,
    "text": "Whoa, watch your head there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.45,
    "endTime": 135.0,
    "text": "Oh be careful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.0,
    "endTime": 137.0,
    "text": "Is this where you live?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.0,
    "endTime": 140.5,
    "text": "Yep, just me and Abu. Come and go as we please."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.5,
    "endTime": 142.41,
    "text": "That sounds fabulous."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.41,
    "endTime": 147.5,
    "text": "Well, it's not much, but it's got a great view."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.5,
    "endTime": 150.7,
    "text": "Wow, the palace looks pretty amazing, huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.0,
    "endTime": 153.45,
    "text": "Oh, it's wonderful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.45,
    "endTime": 158.5,
    "text": "But I wonder what it would be like to live there and have servants, and valets."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.5,
    "endTime": 163.28,
    "text": "Sure, people who tell you where to go and how to dress."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.28,
    "endTime": 164.5,
    "text": "That's better than here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.5,
    "endTime": 167.34,
    "text": "You're always scraping for food and ducking the guards."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.34,
    "endTime": 169.357,
    "text": "You're not free to make your own choices."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.5,
    "endTime": 171.0,
    "text": "Sometimes you feel so..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.0,
    "endTime": 171.8,
    "text": "You're just."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.0,
    "endTime": 177.8,
    "text": "Trapped."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.8,
    "endTime": 184.0,
    "text": "Your majesty, I am Prince Ali Ababwa. Just let her meet me, I will win your daughter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.0,
    "endTime": 189.7,
    "text": "How dare you? All of you, standing around deciding my future."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.7,
    "endTime": 193.053,
    "text": "I am not a prize to be won."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.053,
    "endTime": 195.0,
    "text": "Oh dear."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.0,
    "endTime": 198.22,
    "text": "You're right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.22,
    "endTime": 205.5,
    "text": "You aren't just some prize to be won. You should be free to make your own choice. I'll go now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.5,
    "endTime": 206.5,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.5,
    "endTime": 208.11,
    "text": "What, what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.0,
    "endTime": 209.5,
    "text": "How?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.5,
    "endTime": 211.2,
    "text": "How are you doing that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.2,
    "endTime": 213.54999999999998,
    "text": "It's a magic carpet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.0,
    "endTime": 216.756,
    "text": "It's lovely."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.756,
    "endTime": 220.28,
    "text": "You don't wanna go for a ride, do you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.28,
    "endTime": 223.19,
    "text": "We could get out of the palace, see the world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.19,
    "endTime": 224.26,
    "text": "Is it safe?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.26,
    "endTime": 227.375,
    "text": "Sure, do you trust me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.375,
    "endTime": 228.5,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.5,
    "endTime": 232.17,
    "text": "Do you trust me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.0,
    "endTime": 242.5,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.5,
    "endTime": 244.478,
    "text": "♪ A whole new world ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.478,
    "endTime": 246.3,
    "text": "♪ A whole new world ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.3,
    "endTime": 248.3,
    "text": "♪ That's where we'll be ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.3,
    "endTime": 250.60000000000002,
    "text": "♪ That's where we'll be ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.6,
    "endTime": 252.31,
    "text": "♪ A thrilling chase ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.31,
    "endTime": 254.7,
    "text": "♪ A wondrous place ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.7,
    "endTime": 263.26,
    "text": "♪ For you and me ♪"
  }
]